flowchart TD

A[User types note into text field] --> B[User clicks Save button]

B --> C[Browser prevents default form submit]
C --> D[JavaScript event handler triggered]

D --> E["Create note object<br/>{ content, date }"]
E --> F[Add note to local notes array]

F --> G[Redraw notes list on page]
E --> H["Send POST request to server<br/>/notes"]

H --> I[Server receives request]
I --> J[Server stores note in database]
J --> K[Server sends JSON response]

K --> L[Browser receives response]
L --> M[Console may log response]